far as near from me He kept me safe from danger, and removed
discomforts, till I entered the Sacred sanctuary of the brother of His
Apostle, blessings of Allah be on him and on his children. 

As you enter the city, recite: 

Praise be to Allah who made me enter His blessed preinct, Which
has been sanctified and selected by Allah For the successor of His
Prophet, O Allah, therefore, let him take notice of (my arrival).
When you reach the first gate say: 

O Allah I stand at Your door, set foot in Your courtyard, hold fast to
Your rope, ask for Your mercy, apply to Your friend and
representative, Your blessings be on him so welcome my visitation
and give favourable answer to my prayer.

Whey you reach the gate of the courtyard, say:

O Allah! Surely this sanctuary is Your sanctuary and this place is
