know better than me about it and my secrets and whisperings All
Praise be to Allah, the Benefactor, the Benovelent, Who, by His
Grace, has made easy for me the visitation of my master and has not
prevented me from his visitation and neither has He repelled me
from his mastership, rather He has favoured and granted. O Allah!
As You have obliged me by his recognition then include me among
his adherents and cause me to enter Paradise by his intercession, O the most Merciful of all those who show Mercy.

When you reach the courtyard say: 

Praise be to Allah Who honoured me with insight in the divine
