be on him. Peace be on the possessor of tranquility Peace be on him
who is resting in Medina. Peace be on him whom Allah helped and
assisted. Peace be on Abdul Qasim Mohammad, son of Abdullah.
Mercy and blessings of Allah be on him.

Now enter the canopy and enter with the right foot forward and
