Merciful of all who show mercy!

Then kiss the Zari and stand with your back to the Qibla and face
towards the grave of Imam Husain (a.s.) and recite:

Peace be on you, O Abu Abdullah. Peace be on you, O the son of the
Apostle of Allah. Peace be on you, O the son of the commander of
