اَلسَّلامُ عَلى اَبِي الْاَئِمَّةِ وَمَعْدِنِ النُّبُوَّة It is the 7th Ziyarat in the ‘Tohfa’ of Allamah Majlisi (r.a.). The author of ‘Mazaar-e-Qadeem’ says that it is special for the eve of 27th Rajab, as we have mentioned in the book of ‘Hadiyyat-uz-Zaaereen.’

