you must recite the following Dua: 

In the name of Allah, the most merciful, most kind. Indeed my sins
are great, nothing remains except hope in Your forgiveness. I have
come with the tools of depravity to You so I ask You, O Allah, what I
do not deserve and I seek from You what I am not worthy of. O
Allah, if You punish me then it will be due to my sins, You will not
have wronged me in the least. If You forgive me then it is because
You are the most merciful, O my master. O Allah, You are what You
are and I am what I am; You are the one who forgives repeatedly, I
