and through you Allah will avenge the blood of every believer which is sought and through you, the earth bears trees and because of
you, the earth brings out its fruits and because of you the sky sends down rain and sustenance and through you, Allah removes the
misfortunes and through you, Allah sends down water and through you, the earth which bears your bodies glorifies Allah and the mountains remain firm on their place. 

The intention of the Lord is in the fate of His affairs which come down towards you and are emanated from your houses and the judgements for the servants
originate from them. May the people be cursed who killed you and the people who opposed you and the people who denied your
