      {
        "title": "Second Ziyarat of Imam Hussain(as)",
        "arabic":
            """Shaykh Kulaini (a.r.) has narrated from Imam Ali Naqi (a.s.) that he (a.s.) said:

Recite the following at the grave of Imam Husain (a.s.):
اَلسَّلامُ عَلَيْكَ يا اَبا عَبْدِاللهِ، اَلسَّلامُ عَلَيْكَ يا حُجَّةَ اللهِ فِي اَرْضِهِ وَشاهِدَهُ عَلى خَلْقِهِ، اَلسَّلامُ عَلَيْكَ يا بْنَ رَسُولِ اللهِ، اَلسَّلامُ عَلَيْكَ يا بْنَ عَليِّ الْمُرْتَضى، اَلسَّلامُ عَلَيْكَ يا بْنَ فاطِمَةَ الزَّهْراءِ، اَشْهَدُ اَنَّكَ قَدْ اَقَمْتَ الصَّلاةَ وَآتَيْتَ الزَّكاةَ، وَاَمَرْتَ بِالْمَعْرُوفِ وَنَهَيْتَ عَنِ الْمُنْكَرِ، وَجاهَدْتَ فِي سَبيلِ اللهِ حَتّى اَتاكَ الْيَقينُ، فَصَلّى اللهُ عَلَيْكَ حَيّاً وَميّتاً

After that place your right cheek on the grave and say:
اَشْهَدُ اَنَّكَ عَلى بَيِّنَة مِنْ رَبِّكَ، جِئْتُ مُقِرّاً بِالذُّنُوبِ لِتَشْفَعَ لي عِنْدَ رَبِّكَ يَا بْنَ رَسُولِ اللهِ

Then remember each of the Imams (a.s.) by his name and say:
اَشْهَدُ اَنَّكُمْ حُجَجُ اللهِ

Then say:
اُكْتُبْ لي عِنْدَكَ ميثاقاً وَعَهْداً اِنّي اَتَيْتُكَ مُجَدِّداً الْميثاقَ فَاشْهَدْ لي عِنْدَ رَبِّكَ اِنَّكَ اَنْتَ الشّاهِدُ""",
        "translation":
            """Shaykh Kulaini (a.r.) has narrated from Imam Ali Naqi (a.s.) that he (a.s.) said:

Recite the following at the grave of Imam Husain (a.s.): 

Peace be on you, O Abu Abdullah. Peace be on you, O the proof of Allah in His earth and His witness upon His creation. Peace be on you, O the son of the Apostle of Allah. Peace be on you, O the son of Ali al-Murtaza. Peace be on you, O the son of Fatemah Zehra. 

I bear witness that you established the prayer and gave the poor-due and enjoined the good and forbade the evil and strove in the way of Allah till death overtook you. Then may Allah bless you in life and in death

After that place your right cheek on the grave and say:

I believe that you are on a proof from your Lord. I come to you,attesting to my sins so that you, O the son of the Apostle of Allah, may intercede for me near your Lord.

Then remember each of the Imams (a.s.) by his name and say:

I bear witness that you are the proofs of Allah

Then Say:

I believe that you are on a proof from your Lord. I come to you,attesting to my sins so that you, O the son of the Apostle of Allah,may intercede for me near your Lord

Then remember each of the Imams (a.s.) by his name and say:

I bear witness that you are the proofs of Allah

Then say:

I do write for me a covenant and pledge with you that I have come to you renewing the covenant. Then bear witness for me near your Lord. Surely you are the witness.""",
