      {
        "title": "Fourth Ziyarat of Imam Hussain(a.s)",
        "arabic":
            """It is related from Muawiyah bin Ammar that he asked Imam Sadiq (a.s.): What should I recite when I go for the Ziyarat of Imam Husain (a.s.)? He (a.s.) replied: 

