After this come back to the head side of Imam Husain (a.s.) and supplicate for yourself, your family, parents and brothers, because all invocations and supplications are accepted in this shrine.leader of the women of the Universe. Peace be on you. O helpers of Abu Muhammad al-Hasan b. ‘Ali, the friend of Allah and advisor to the people. Peace be on you, O helpers of Abu ‘Abd Allah. May my father and mother be sacrificed for you. You are pure and the ground in which you were buried also became purified. All of you achieved tremendous success! I wish I had been with you, I would have triumphed with you.""",
