the Mankind Peace be on you , O Choice of Allah! Peace be on you, O
Mohammad son of Abdullah, the last of the prophets, Peace be on
you, O Commander of the faithful, Ali son of Abu Talib, and the
Successor of the Apostle of Allah Peace be on you, O Fatimah, the
Leader of the women of the worlds, Peace be on you, O the
grandsons of the Prophet of Mercy. and the leaders of the youth of
Paradise Peace be on you, O Ali son of Husayn the leader of
worshippers, O coolness of investigating eyes, Peace be on you O Mohammad son of Ali, O the explorer of knowledge after the
prophet Peace be on you, O Ja’far son of Mohammed, the truthful,
the benign, the trustworthy, Peace be on you, O Mosa son of Ja’far,
the pure, the purified Peace be on you, O Ali son of Moosa, the
pleased, the gratified. Peace be on you, O Mohammad son of Ali, the
pious one Peace be on you, on Ali son of Mohammad, the pure, the
